comment: Collison (SAC) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Collison (SAC) pushes Lillard (POR) and affects his SQBR. This is correctly ruled a non-shooting foul.
Collison (SAC) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) strips the ball without affecting Gay's (SAC) SQBR.
Gay (SAC) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Afflalo (SAC) jumps vertically and any contact is initiated by Harkless (POR) on the driving shot attempt.
Plumlee (POR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact that does not affect Cousins' (SAC) driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) beats Cousins (SAC) to the spot and is firming up on contact. The screen contact causes movement by McCollum.
RATR shows Collison (SAC) has part of his hand under the ball when he brings it to a pause and continues his dribble.
Plumlee (POR) makes contact with Gay's (SAC) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
From the available angles, Temple (SAC) does not make contact that affects McCollum's (POR) shooting motion.
Lillard (POR) makes contact with Collison's (SAC) legs that affects his FOM to the loose ball.
Gay (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on the driving shot attempt by Leonard (POR).
Leonard (POR) and Cousins (SAC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Cousins (SAC) commits a take foul on Crabbe (POR).
Leonard (POR) makes incidental contact with Cousins (SAC) after the release of the shot.
